<div type="definition">
<p>MONEY to be PAID as PUNISHMENT.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The general word for a fine is fá 罰, and the word refers to fines of any kind.</p>
<p>2. Zī 貲 refers to a minor fine for a minor offence according to SHUOWEN and also in the Qin laws.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>罰款</p>
<p>罰鍰</p>
<p>刑罰</p>
<p>處罰</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
